@startuml
title Query Loop Main Cycle - Turn States

skinparam backgroundColor #F7F1E6
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 130
skinparam defaultFontName Georgia
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam TitleFontSize 19
skinparam TitleFontColor #161616
skinparam NoteFontSize 12
skinparam ArrowFontSize 12
skinparam ArrowColor #5E5A53
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #F2E9D9
  BorderColor #1D1D1D
  FontColor #161616
  ArrowColor #5E5A53
  StartColor #8C2721
  EndColor #161616
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #F5EBDD
  BorderColor #8C2721
  FontColor #7B1E1E
}

[*] --> Prepare

state "Prepare\nprefetch / boundary /\nbudget / snip / microcompact" as Prepare #F2E9D9
state "Blocking Check\nhook / budget / guard" as Blocking #F5EBDD
state "Stream Model" as Model #EFE6D8
state "Tool Execution\nStreamingToolExecutor" as Tools #EFE6D8
state "Append Turn Effects" as Effects #F2E9D9
state "Stop Hooks" as Stop #E8DDD0
state "Surface Error" as Error #F5EBDD

Prepare --> Blocking : context ready
Blocking --> Error : limit hit / hook block
Blocking --> Model : ok
Model --> Tools : tool_use
Model --> Effects : text only
Tools --> Effects : results merged
Effects --> Prepare : follow-up turn
Effects --> Stop : stable completion
Stop --> [*]
Error --> [*]

note right of Prepare
  Every turn starts here.
  The loop re-enters Prepare
  after a follow-up turn,
  after recovery, and after
  compact rebuilds.
end note

note right of Tools
  Tool-result reinjection
  is what keeps the loop
  stateful across turns.
end note

@enduml
